  <div id="text-content_7FF2BAF0-22E2-0135-8D32-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you set your rubric for grading, the rubric points will be automatically populated in the grade field. Otherwise, you can enter the grade from the rubric manually.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
